      "span_text": "Among the remaining 6 genes, DHRS7C is located in the sarcoplasmic reticulum of the heart and skeletal muscle  , although it is predicted to be secreted by WoLF PSORT. The other 5 genes-CTLA2A in the lung, MUP19 in the liver and WFDC15B, SERPINA1F and DEFB29 in the kidney have not been reported to be secreted in currently available publications."
